        <item>
            <title>Galaxy S24 Ultra 外形設計曝光，疑棄用圓邊機身改用午餐肉風格</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/galaxy-s24-ultra-leaks/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=galaxy-s24-ultra-leaks</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/08/galaxy-s24-ultra-leaks/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 08 Oct 2023 06:42:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1197742</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>擁有超強攝影功能及外殼採用環保材料製成的 Samsung Galaxy S23 Ultra 已於今年 2 月推出，而下一代旗艦機 Galaxy S24 Ultra 預計於明年初登場。近日就有爆料者利用已掌握的消息來源，製作了 Galaxy S24 Ultra 的外形設計渲染圖。渲染圖展示了 Galaxy S24 Ultra 或將放棄使用圓邊機身，轉為較四方、較平面的機身。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.35.jpg"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.35-694x412.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="412" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.35-694x412.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.35-1280x759.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.35-768x455.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.35.jpg 1376w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.41.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.41-694x419.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="419" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.41-694x419.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.41-1280x773.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.41-768x464.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.41.jpg 1368w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.45.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.45-694x431.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="431" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.45-694x431.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.45-1280x794.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.45-768x476.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-12.22.45.jpg 1370w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>外媒《smartprix》報道表示，雖然 Galaxy S24 Ultra 繼續配備 6.8 吋大熒幕，但邊框尺寸方面縮小了許多，是所有智慧型手機上最窄的邊框之一。而該裝置將配備 WQHD+ 分辨率熒幕，預計採用平面設計。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_smartprix_main_1696009724186.jpg 950w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1197771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/galaxy_s24_ultra_leaked_renders_onleaks_1696009309214.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1197751" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-10.01.52-694x392.png" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-10.01.52-694x392.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-10.01.52-1280x722.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-10.01.52-768x433.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-06-10.01.52.png 1372w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">（圖片來源：<a href="https://www.smartprix.com/bytes/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-first-look/">smartprix</a>）</p><p>另外，手機設有四鏡頭設置，容納多個感應器，又為 S-Pen 保留了專用皮套，迎合重視手寫筆功能的使用者，並且疑似在右側邊緣添加 UWB 天線。</p><p>外媒及爆料者又估計，Galaxy S24 Ultra 的尺寸約為 162.3 x 79 x 8.7 毫米，採用鈦金屬框架，預計將使設備重量減輕 1 克，總重量為 233 克。而電池尺寸很可能保持在 5000mAh，並輔以 45W 快充支援。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="in" dir="ltr">Galaxy S24:<br />147 × 70.6 × 7.6mm 6.2&quot; 168g 4000mAh<br />FHD+ resolution, 2500nit, 25w</p><p>Galaxy S24+<br />158.5 × 75.9 × 7.7mm 6.7&quot; 195g 4900mAh<br />WQHD+ resolution, 2500nit, 45w</p><p>Galaxy S24 Ultra:<br />162.3 × 79 × 8.6mm 6.8&quot; 233g 5000mAh<br />WQHD+ resolution, 2500nit, 45w</p><p>&mdash; ICE UNIVERSE (@UniverseIce) <a href="https://twitter.com/UniverseIce/status/1707670666290532628?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">September 29, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.gadgets360.com/mobiles/news/galaxy-s24-ultra-design-specifications-revealed-leaked-cad-renders-4436803">gadgets360</a>、<a href="https://www.smartprix.com/bytes/samsung-galaxy-s24-ultra-first-look/">smartprix</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
